cs.NE, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.SY

This paper proposes modifications to the traditional hypermutations operator in Artificial Immune Systems (AIS) to improve its efficiency during the exploitation phase. As such, the paper is likely to belong to the Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Machine Learning (cs.LG) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper involves optimization problems, which could place it in the Data Structures and Algorithms (cs.DS) sub-category. Finally, the paper proposes modifications to improve the efficiency of AIS, which could place it in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
